15dd4af"},{"id":"0bc62e2ef8","type":"paragraph","text":"中一加强思想领导，造成班上空气阴森森的、杀气逼人。有的哭了，有的人不满他们的批评，在班会上公开反对，则被那些党团分子认为有政治问题。要检查他们的档案，这顶白橡皮帽子，不知坑杀了多少正直的人。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"36922a5ad5","type":"paragraph","text":"万永钦(物理系学生)大字报：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"f04ef05bc6","type":"subtitle","text":"科长遗嘱","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"2010af428b","type":"paragraph","text":"余致力侵犯人权凡40年，其目的在求取消学生之自由平等。积40年之经验，深知欲达到此目的，必须唤（起）党团员及学校以老爷待我之应声虫，共同奋斗。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"d5229ac2ee","type":"paragraph","text":"现在压制尚未成功，凡我们党团员，务须依照余所著，收员方略、暗收大纲、独裁主义、及第一次开黑名单的人权宣言，继续努力，以求贯彻，最近主张，开“报复会议”，及废除民主与自由。尤须于最短期间，促其实现，是所至嘱。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"cc6d22fced","type":"paragraph","text":" 学生科长人事科长  签名档案科长（大字报作者署名：腾文公）","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"140a01dbee","type":"paragraph","text":"林绍述(云南大学历史系一年学生，共产党员)在“民主墙”上写道：","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"c6523bd581","type":"subtitle","text":"看，官僚主义十大罪状","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"03c369d089","type":"paragraph","text":"一声不响，二目无光，三餐不食，四肢无力。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"9403d0a25d","type":"paragraph","text":"五官不正，六亲无靠，七穷不通，八面威风。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"b37e812f60","type":"paragraph","text":"九坐无事，十分无用。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"c9698b411b","type":"paragraph","text":"党委书记同志，你太辛苦了！","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"a6b7b44e48","type":"paragraph","text":"党委书记真辛苦，深更半夜忙工作，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"45a8f8df6f","type":"paragraph","text":"肿眼疲乏无所谓，可谓鞠躬瘁。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"c5b8b6e03e","type":"paragraph","text":"为何时间飞似箭，流水会议数不完，","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"0ad3d5040b","type":"paragraph","text":"左听汇报右打转，了如指掌真会管。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"765c9bdc3d","type":"paragraph","text":"先订计划后总结，原则指示断无绝。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"61e484d91e","type":"paragraph","text":"中心工作是教学，灵活工作必须作。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"ecdb54272b","type":"paragraph","text":"教学质量低且劣，不尊师来不团结。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"94b0a6f9fd","type":"paragraph","text":"知识分子问题多，后进层不用说，","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"a8573264b8","type":"paragraph","text":"到校工作有数年，经验多少总有一点，","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"05d2b7fe16","type":"paragraph","text":"头痛会医头，脚痛会医脚。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"e215e63a4e","type":"paragraph","text":"党课无血无肉，保险无错误。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"22ec8e509d","type":"paragraph","text":"教学不管不要紧，有马列主义作资本，","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"be2717df5a","type":"paragraph","text":"不愁吃来不愁穿，荣华富贵万万年。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"6b0d936a54","type":"paragraph","text":"秦树基(云大中文系二年级学生)说：","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"b31442c121","type":"subtitle","text":"这个班早已成了黑暗王国了","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"d6baa40e01","type":"paragraph","text":"一年来的情况，这个班，早已成了一个黑暗王国了。……在这里，新中国，自由中国的气味嗅不到，人与人间的关系是戒备，倾轧和陷害。这里充满了庸俗和自私，充满了腐臭。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"1f977a07c2","type":"paragraph","text":"我们班上真正正义的，纯洁的、不抓人害人的青年，是你们压迫的对象。因为刘（鼎澄）不反对你，你们便想把他拉过去作顺民，孤立我。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"3aa4a7e307","type":"paragraph","text":"提意见的人加上“落后”、“有抵触情绪”的帽子，当然，你们掌权，我们没有办法。但你们错了还不承认，许多青年在你们的压迫下抬不起头来。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"5db247a6fe","type":"subtitle","text":"我们不能当新中国的主人，得到的是压迫","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"04e1866e5b","type":"paragraph","text":"甚么温暖的大家庭，甚么集体，甚么互助友爱，这些词如果跟我们这个班连缀在一起的话，是对这些美好的名词的一个污辱。所谓的领导者们，你们不是在领导，你们是在进行统治。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"780f32925e","type":"paragraph","text":"我们青年幻想的新中国是自由、民主，要我们关心集体，但我们受排斥，怎能不自悲。我们不能当新中国的主人，得到的是统治、压迫。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"c7363a044e","type":"subtitle","text":"入党团是一个学习虚伪，学习当顺民的过程","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"ed66f3caa5","type":"paragraph","text":"“反对人为的制造党、团、群差别”（师院反动标语）是对的，如我校的党、团、群就有差别。“反对一党专政”，这可能是他感到本单位的党，不听取别人的意见。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"3e0f9cf974","type":"paragraph","text":"章乃器说得对：共产党员是什么特殊材料制成的呢？岂有此理，根本讲不通。共产党员也是人，有什么特殊？他们也是肉做成的。要说特殊，“享乐在先，吃苦在后”，这就是特殊。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"9e1ae729c5","type":"paragraph","text":"在接收党团员时，考虑条件就完全违背了党、团章的精神。入党团不是受一次真正的考验，而是一个学习虚伪的过程，学习当顺民的过程……因为这种风气，入团的人都必须学会这一套。想想，真正有正义感的人如何看得惯！","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"fb956789b9","type":"paragraph","text":"刘文汶(云大历史系一年级学生)在平时散布说：","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"ffa2d31b77","type":"subtitle","text":"美国是钢老虎。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"aeba16c660","type":"paragraph","text":"美国装备比苏联好，是第一流的装备。并不是说美国不行，美国还是不错，第五次战役中（在朝鲜）美军就把志愿军引到箩篼头去。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"fe1ca86f92","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的报纸对美国报导得不真实，美国的生产力还是很高。人家生产一个“子耳朵”比我们的大腿还大。","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"ee806bd0a9","type":"paragraph","text":"杨成武指挥犯了错误，打败仗。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"ee6cbe655b","type":"paragraph","text":"志愿军新兵投降的很多。","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"d28e04f1fe","type":"paragraph","text":"志愿担架大队刚过江听到炮火凶就跑回来了，怕死。","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"9d3c238cca","type":"paragraph","text":"当兵很苦，你不信去问问班上复员军人那个还愿意上前线？","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"8db0b2cb72","type":"paragraph","text":"当兵我抵触得很，随便问那个都不愿再去，我回到江律就把衣服全染黑了。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"80071669d4","type":"paragraph","text":"政府对转业军人不照顾。我们回来在万县碰到好多复员军人穿得很烂，向我们要烟吃。有个转业军人没有工作，把军功奖章挂起去卖水果。","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"5a5e2fe117","type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石精神很好，说话很有感染力。解放前他在成都对军校廿三期学生讲了十五分钟的话，他哭了，学生也都痛哭流涕。他说：“同志们！不要悲观，不要失望，我们现在还有一二百万军队，好几省土地，回想辛亥革命当年，我们几百人打下了全中国。我到台湾去了，你们跟我打一仗，我一定派飞机来接你们。”后来果然派了四百架飞机来，但被胡宗南拿去运他的军队去了，所以那些学生全部战死了。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"02e1b6d44f","type":"paragraph","text":"我早就有远大的抱负，解放前我想推翻国民党，解放后我又想推翻共产党。我考查了阶级力量，农民要求土地，这个问题共产党已经解决了；工人，共产党抓得更紧；资产阶级力量小；知识分子又怕死，因此，革命条件不成熟。","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"c6f07ab991","type":"subtitle","text":"档案制度是特务政治","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"bfbaffb4f5","type":"paragraph","text":"在鸣放中他又在大会上拍桌子大骂：","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"d37d6966b3","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党的档案制度是特务的政治，党棍政治，甚至比国民党的特务政治还厉害。","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"3f3c6ecff3","type":"paragraph","text":"学校党委制流弊多，我建议取消党委制。我认为党委退出学校去，党不要过问学校的事情。","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"a145d59bb3","type":"paragraph","text":"历次运动都要死人，不死人才奇怪，这是为什么？难道个个都该死？","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"12e6107e03","type":"paragraph","text":"张永康","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"4df923c0c7","type":"paragraph","text":"云大物理系二年级学生张永康说：","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"4de2ee8286","type":"paragraph","text":"打倒共产党为何不可呢？","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"46f121cc18","type":"paragraph","text":"匈牙利事件发生在中国，我也要干他几个。","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"bd8a14adcb","type":"paragraph","text":"打倒共产党有什么不可以呢？党委在学校没有必要。","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"e69ef6e4fd","type":"paragraph","text":"章 忠 实","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"664591f416","type":"paragraph","text":"农学系学生章忠实说：","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"01b8eb74a7","type":"paragraph","text":"团组织是卑污龌龊的","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"45bf62db61","type":"paragraph","text":"团组织是虚伪、卑污、龌龊的。","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"},{"id":"ca35b642f6","type":"paragraph","text":"人民民主专政是对地主、民主资产阶级专政，那么为什么农民要改造？","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af"}],"page":{"id":"6098d77ab3","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32015dd4af","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}